cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.DS 

This paper deals with source coding and side information, which are topics typically studied in the information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the control of side information, which falls under the sub-category of signal processing (cs.SI). The use of in-block memory is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and data structures (cs.DS), which could also be relevant to this paper.
